<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS SAVIOUR PILOT ME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Isu ei puiin,
 Damsung tuilien laka hin;
 Ka ma ah tuia kinawk,
 Suongpi guk, nga lauhum tam,
 Mun hetna Nang apat hung,
 Lalpa Isu ei puiin.

[V2]
 2. Nu'n a cha a thepbih bang,
 Tuipi lien na hihhai thei;
 Tui kinawkin Na thu awi,
 &quot;Haiin, tuilien na tih tieng,&quot;
 Lal mak tuichunga thunei,
 Lalpa Isu ei puiin!

[V3]
 3. Luipi pang chuh ka naih tieng,
 Tui kinawk lauhum gi leh;
 Chawlhna nuom ka tun kuonin,
 Na awma ka kingaih tieng;
 &quot;Lau ki'n, ka cha ka hun tu'i,
 Ti a Na gen ka za dem?</lyrics>
<hymn_number>90</hymn_number>
</song>